FBIS3-30489 "dreeu024_y_94006" FBIS-EEU-94-024 Document Type:Daily Report 4 Feb 1994 YUGOSLAVIA Macedonia Diplomatic Relations Established With Czechs LD0302180694 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in Serbo-Croatian 1657 GMT 3 Feb 94 LD0302180694 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service Language: Serbo-Croatian Article Type:BFN [Text] Skopje, 3 Feb (TANJUG) -- The Czech Republic informed the former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia today that the government in Prague has reached a decision on the establishment of full diplomatic relations with Macedonia at ambassadorial level, it was announced in Skopje today. Commenting on the news disclosed in Moscow on the establishment of diplomatic relations at the level of embassies between the Russian Federation and Macedonia, Russian envoy in Skopje Yuriy Petrovich said in a statement for Skopje Radio that Russia would mediate in the Macedonian-Greek dispute if asked to do so.
